headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Automotive Supplies and Vehicle Discounts
content:
To help players gear up for the newest Race Series, we're proud to offer discounts on all sorts of automotive supplies, as well as a selection of speedy vehicles, including:

- Garage Properties (excluding Vehicle Warehouse) – 40% off
- Dinka Jester Classic (Sports) – 30% off
- Pegassi Infernus Classic (Sports Classic) – 30% off
- Ocelot Ardent (Sports Classic) – 30% off

And more! Check out the Rockstar Newswire for more details.
